{"tid":1322714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大華裔病毒學家邱香果　遭當地警方帶離國家實驗室","createTime":"2019-07-16T04:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T18:41:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b09f036ea2b68d93ca5fde1eb00a370e6a3f5000","tid":1322714,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:29:47.000Z","msg":"加拿大華裔病毒學家邱香果 遭當地警方帶離國家實驗室<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190715/s00004/1563154084555/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E9%82%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%9E%9C-%E9%81%AD%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%B8%B6%E9%9B%A2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97%E5%AE%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190715%2Fs00004%2F1563154084555%2F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A3%2594%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%259E%259C-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%25AE%25A4&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=fdb78eb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190715%2Fs00004%2F1563154084555%2F%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%258B%25BF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%25A3%2594%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2582%25B1%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%259E%259C-%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E9%259B%25A2%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%25AE%25A4&h=35dcb372\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190715/s00004/1563154084555/%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%8F%AF%E8%A3%94%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E5%AD%B8%E5%AE%B6%E9%82%B1%E9%A6%99%E6%9E%9C-%E9%81%AD%E7%95%B6%E5%9C%B0%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%B8%B6%E9%9B%A2%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%AF%A6%E9%A9%97%E5%AE%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n【20:00】外交部發言人耿爽表示，中國駐多倫多總領館尚未接到有關中國公民的通報。他說，若事件涉及中國公民，中國使領館將依法向他們提供領事協助，保障他們的正當合法權益。<br />\n<br />\n【09:59】加拿大廣播公司引述消息報道，加拿大華裔病毒學家邱香果夫婦及其多名來自中國的學生，本月5日被當地警方以「違反相關政策」（policy breach）為由，帶離位於溫尼辟（Winnipeg）的國家微生物實驗室。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，事件發生前數個月，國家微生物實驗室的資訊科技部門專家，曾進入邱香果的辦公室，並將其電腦帶走。而邱香果夫婦及涉事的一批中國學生被帶離後，國家微生物實驗室已禁止他們進入，當地警方其後於本月8日向實驗室職員說，現時邱香果夫婦正在長期休假，呼籲實驗室職員不要與他們接觸。<br />\n<br />\n溫尼辟的國家微生物實驗室是北美地區少數的4級實驗室，可處理例如伊波拉病毒等嚴重致命病原體。<br />\n<br />\n邱香果是來自天津的細菌學家，1996年前往加拿大攻讀研究生，此後成為魁北克省拉瓦勒大學微生物及傳染病系教授，曾有份協助開發伊波拉病毒治療法「ZMapp」，享負盛名，事發時她在國家微生物實驗室內負責疫苗開發。<br />\n<br />\n現時當地傳媒暫時未能聯絡中國駐當地大使館取得回應。<br />\n<br />\n（加拿大廣播公司）"},{"pid":"2b4931ff74cd4206d995f10e69a5fde61298228e","tid":1322714,"uid":99978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:31:16.000Z","msg":"支那人冇一個係無辜的"},{"pid":"0c41927083c18ecfa540a013a565e6bda5027871","tid":1322714,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T05:10:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52497342afe2fcd314f7b64438ecabc51456afe2","tid":1322714,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd09549f274fc87ff98f054eb30ff5a30a27c72","tid":1322714,"uid":42364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"華裔即係唔係支那籍？<br />\n叫得華裔多數外國籍<br />\n宜家支那衝出黎保佢<br />\n即係一路都係做緊間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96023ae5f395b60da86c0d34140718c1435a9a2f","tid":1322714,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT